ensure right to water and sanitation of marginalized communities of the
district. WAN and partners will work to improve water, sanitation and hygiene
status in school.&nbsp;</span></p><h2><font style="font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial,sans-serif">2. What?</font></h2> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif"></font>&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12pt;">WaterAid aims to transform the lives of poor communities in Siraha District, Nepal, by securing their human right to safe water and sanitation. Over three years, WaterAid will
