mme is the project implementing, which programme outcome(s) will it contribute to, and is it building on previous work at WaterAid?</font></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif">The project will work to understand and address existing
inequalities in WASH. The project will work towards addressing inequalities and
deprivations that marginalized people and individuals are currently facing in
their lives on Water Sanitation and Hygiene (WASH). This project will reach out
to the marginalized communities with equitable access to WASH inclusive
facilities and services, through appropriate approaches and technologies, while
building their institutions, capacities and accountability of local service
providers. Through partner organizations, this will enable the community people
by making them aware of their rights to water and sanitation, build their
capacity to take collective actions, make demands for water and sanitation
services and be represented in decision-making platforms. It will mobilize
local level civil society organizations including citizen centres/forums to
raise unheard voices of the voiceless people.</font></p> <h2><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif"></font><font style="font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial,sans-serif">2. What?</font></h2> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif"></font><strong><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="#ffb612" face="Arial,sans-serif">--- Guidance text, please delete down to the next heading ---</font></strong></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif">This section should cover:</font></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><strong><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif">Project theme</font></strong><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;– What are the main WASH areas that this project focuses on and the main activities that will be implemented?</font></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><strong><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif">Estimated cost</font></strong><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;– Highlight if any funds have already been secured, or if this is fully unfunded.</font></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><strong><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif">Estimated timeframe</font></strong><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;– Not a start / end date but approximate length of project (in months)</font></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><strong><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif">Existing WaterAid experience</font></strong><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;– New innovation / less than 2 years’ experience / more than 2 years’ experience</font></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif">The main WASH area that
